      • Improvement

        public Improvement(java.lang.String name,
                   java.lang.String id,
                   int intPriority,
                   ImprovementCollaborator leader,
                   Request approvedRequest,
                   java.lang.String processCode)

        Improvement

        Description: Constructs a new improvement and transformation project with the specified name, ID, priority, leader, approved request, and process name.

        Preconditions:

        • The name parameter must be a String representing the name of the improvement and transformation project.
        • The id parameter must be a String representing the ID of the improvement and transformation project.
        • The intPriority parameter must be an integer representing the priority of the improvement and transformation project (1 for urgent, 2 for high, 3 for medium, and 4 for low).
        • The leader parameter must be an ImprovementCollaborator object representing the leader of the improvement and transformation project.
        • The approvedRequest parameter must be a Request object representing the approved request associated with the improvement and transformation project.
        • The processCode parameter must be a String representing the name of the process associated with the improvement and transformation project.

        Postconditions:

        • A new improvement and transformation project is created with the provided name, ID, priority, leader, approved request, and process name.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the improvement and transformation project.
        id - The ID of the improvement and transformation project.
        intPriority - An int which represents the priority level of the improvement and transformation project (1 for urgent, 2 for high, 3 for medium, and 4 for low).
        leader - The leader of the improvement and transformation project.
        approvedRequest - The approved request associated with the improvement and transformation project.
        processCode - The name of the process associated with the improvement and transformation project.
